Package: arl
Type: Package
Title: A Lisp for R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("William", "Brannon", email = "will.brannon@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1435-8535"))
Author: William Brannon
Maintainer: William Brannon <will.brannon@gmail.com>
Description: Arl is a Scheme-inspired Lisp embedded in R. It provides macros,
    tail-call optimization, and first-class interoperability with R functions and
    data structures. Implemented in pure R with no compiled code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
